{"tid":2328372,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊度自認思想開放：阿仙奴的確缺乏創造型中場","createTime":"2020-12-16T13:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T15:44:24.000Z","uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ea74db973294e56e4cca3b3ad8a0294a4ded5f4f","tid":2328372,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴技術總監伊度 (Edu Gaspar) 在球迷論壇上表示，球隊在冬季轉會窗的首要目標，是購入具創造力的中場球員。<br />\n<br />\n伊度說：「我們清楚自己想要什麼，就是一名有創造力的中場球員，球隊現在缺乏這樣的球員。」<br />\n<br />\n談到球隊近況低迷時，伊度表示：「我想盡可能對你們坦誠一點，也喜歡聽你們的聲音。作為一個巴西人，我思想很開放。」<br />\n<br />\n「我不會忌諱，現在的處境的確令我們感到不適。」<br />\n<br />\n「關於阿迪達 (Mikel Arteta) 和球員之間有矛盾的故事是虛構的，球員不信任阿迪達也是假的。」"},{"pid":"b0b72c901fe104477346b7d4d81df85720e6475a","tid":2328372,"uid":68,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"奧斯爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049295d100da2317ce52e473aab02043f7b78cf5","tid":2328372,"uid":48247,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"已在陣中..."},{"pid":"0aa9a662f62024325db148f1909282e2c543f11f","tid":2328372,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"比你揀，咁你想買邊個"},{"pid":"0767ffcab4f90a2417276b0047e7d0dcb003af12","tid":2328372,"uid":169487,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"049295d100da2317ce52e473aab02043f7b78cf5","tid":2328372,"uid":48247,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:25:37.000Z","msg":"已在陣中..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"無注册到..."},{"pid":"0baa208da3a5a999d41e719b924f4d129701f730","tid":2328372,"uid":164770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baade4086ff67ec7e09f14c3926c637786bc8dd","tid":2328372,"uid":364041,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-1